flowchart LR
  USER[👤 Guest does something<br/>e.g., uploads a record] --> CLERK[🛎️ Front Desk<br/>route handler]
  CLERK -->|"signs logbook"| LOG[📓 Logbook<br/>audit_log]
  CLERK -->|"says: 'done!'"| USER
  CLERK -.->|"hands off"| BELLHOP[🚶 Bellhop<br/>waitUntil fanout]

  BELLHOP --> BRAIN{🧠 'How do I reach<br/>the recipient?'}
  BRAIN -->|"in their room"| PHONE[☎️ In-app toast]
  BRAIN -->|"out of room"| PAGER[📟 Push notification]
  BRAIN -->|"out of room"| MAIL[✉️ Email]

  WHITEBOARD[📋 Receptionist's<br/>Whiteboard<br/>presence] -.->|"who's where?"| BRAIN
